## المرحلة 3: بدء الخدمات (start)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    START["app.start()"] --> |"asyncio.gather()"| P1["🔀 Transparent Proxy<br/>المنافذ 80, 443"]
    START --> P2["📡 Forward Proxy<br/>المنفذ 8080"]
    START --> P3["🔒 Reverse Proxy<br/>المنفذ 443"]
    START --> ML_LOOP["🧠 ML Maintenance Loop<br/>كل 60 ثانية"]
    START --> API["🔌 API Server<br/>uvicorn على 8000"]

    P1 --> |"asyncio.start_server"| HANDLE1["handle_connection()"]
    P2 --> |"asyncio.start_server"| HANDLE2["handle_connection()"]
    P3 --> |"asyncio.start_server"| HANDLE3["handle_connection()"]
```

